# **Privacy Policy**
**Baab Practice**
Effective Date: January 25, 2025

Baab Practice ("we," "us," or "our") operates the mobile application ("App") that provides Arabic verb learning features. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our App.

---

## **1. Information We Collect**

We do **not** collect personally identifiable information from users of the App. However, the App may store data locally on your device to provide an improved user experience.

### **Automatically Collected Information**
While using the App, we may collect limited non-personal data such as:
- Usage analytics (e.g., time spent on lessons, app feature usage).
- Crash reports and performance data to improve app stability (if enabled).

---

## **2. How We Use Information**

The information collected is used solely to:
- Improve and personalize the user experience.
- Ensure app functionality and performance.
- Fix technical issues and enhance security.

---

## **3. Data Storage and Security**

- All data is stored locally on your device.
- We do not share, sell, or transfer data to third parties.
- The App does not require an internet connection to function, except when fetching content updates (if applicable).

---

## **4. Third-Party Services**

Our App may use third-party services, such as Google Play Services, which may collect data as described in their respective privacy policies. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of those services:
- [Google Play Services Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)

---

## **5. Children's Privacy**

The App is intended for general audiences and does not knowingly collect any personal information from children under 13 years of age.

---

## **6. Your Privacy Choices**

You can manage or delete the locally stored data within the App settings or by uninstalling the App from your device.

---

## **7. Changes to This Privacy Policy**

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the App or on our website. We recommend checking the policy periodically for updates.

---

## **8. Contact Us**

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

**Email:** contact.appsnow@gmail.com
**Website:** [https://shababhsiddique.github.io/arabic-baab/](https://shababhsiddique.github.io/arabic-baab/)

---

**By using the App, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.**

